## AddContentReturn.tags property

All custom tags that have been added \*not including\* the following - `<start>` - `<end>` - `<node>` - `<cursor>` - `<all>` - `<anchor>`

Which are all part of the formal cursor and selection API.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
tags: Tags;
```
